enhanced_by.reason: The toString method relies on the options added to the OptionGroup, which is managed by the addOption method.
The toString method iterates over the options returned by the getOptions method to build its string representation.
The toString method in OptionGroup constructs a string similar to how Option's toString method does, which can inform the assertions for OptionGroup's toString method.
The toString method includes the description of each option, which is obtained via the getDescription method in the Option class.
